radiusClientExtMIB.name: radiusClientExtMIB
radiusClientExtMIB.contactinfo: Steve Colby Postal: ArrowPoint Communications Inc. 50 Nagog Park Acton, Massachusetts 01720 Tel: +1 978-206-3000 option 1 E-Mail: support@arrowpoint.com
radiusClientExtMIB.description: This MIB module describes the ArrowPoint Communications extensions to the client side of the Remote Access Dialin User Service (RADIUS) authentication protocol.

apRadiusClientExtInvalidServerAddresses.name: apRadiusClientExtInvalidServerAddresses
apRadiusClientExtInvalidServerAddresses.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Response packets received from unknown addresses since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtIdentifier.name: apRadiusClientExtIdentifier
apRadiusClientExtIdentifier.description: The NAS-Identifier of the RADIUS client.

apRadiusClientExtDeadTimer.name: apRadiusClientExtDeadTimer
apRadiusClientExtDeadTimer.description: This variable specifies the number of minutes to skip down or not responsing Radius Servers.

apRadiusClientExtProbe.name: apRadiusClientExtProbe
apRadiusClientExtProbe.description: This variable specifies whether the Radius Client will probe down or not responding Radius Servers with probe Access-Request packets to determine their availability.

apRadiusClientExtRetransmitLimit.name: apRadiusClientExtRetransmitLimit
apRadiusClientExtRetransmitLimit.description: This variable specifies the number of times an authentication or accounting request is resent to each radius server after a timeout.

apRadiusClientExtTimeout.name: apRadiusClientExtTimeout
apRadiusClientExtTimeout.description: This variable specifies the interval the Radius Client will wait for the Radius Server to reply to an Authentication or Accounting Request.

apRadiusClientExtSourceIpAddress.name: apRadiusClientExtSourceIpAddress
apRadiusClientExtSourceIpAddress.description: This variable specifies the source IP Address of the interface used by the Radius Client.

apRadiusClientExtServerTable.name: apRadiusClientExtServerTable
apRadiusClientExtServerTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the RADIUS servers with which the client shares a secret.

apRadiusClientExtServerEntry.name: apRadiusClientExtServerEntry
apRadiusClientExtServerEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) representing a RADIUS server with which the client shares a secret.

apRadiusClientExtAddress.name: apRadiusClientExtAddress
apRadiusClientExtAddress.description: The IP address of the RADIUS server referred to in this table entry.

apRadiusClientExtRoundTripTime.name: apRadiusClientExtRoundTripTime
apRadiusClientExtRoundTripTime.description: The total roundtrip time of the last packet sent between the client and the RADIUS server referred to in this table entry.

apRadiusClientExtAccessRequests.name: apRadiusClientExtAccessRequests
apRadiusClientExtAccessRequests.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Request packets sent to this server since client start-up. This does not include retransmissions.

apRadiusClientExtAccessRetransmissions.name: apRadiusClientExtAccessRetransmissions
apRadiusClientExtAccessRetransmissions.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Request packets retransmitted to the same server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtAccessAccepts.name: apRadiusClientExtAccessAccepts
apRadiusClientExtAccessAccepts.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Accept packets received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtAccessRejects.name: apRadiusClientExtAccessRejects
apRadiusClientExtAccessRejects.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Reject packets received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtAccessChallenges.name: apRadiusClientExtAccessChallenges
apRadiusClientExtAccessChallenges.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Challenge packets received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccessResponse.name: apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccessResponses
apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccessResponse.description: The total number of malformed RADIUS Access-Response packets received from this server since client start-up. Bad authenticators are not included as malformed access responses.

apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationBadAuthen.name: apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationBadAuthenticators
apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationBadAuthen.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Response packets containing invalid authenticators received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationPendingRe.name: apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationPendingRequests
apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationPendingRe.description: The total number of RADIUS Access-Request packets destined for this server that have not yet timed out or received a response. This variable is incremented when an Access-Request is sent and decremented due to a timeout or retransmission.

apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationTimeouts.name: apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationTimeouts
apRadiusClientExtAuthenticationTimeouts.description: The total number of authentication timeouts to this server since client startup. After a timeout the client may retry to the same server, send to a different server, or give up. A retry to the same server is counted as a retransmit as well as a timeout. A send to a different server is counted as a Request as well as a timeout.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingRequests.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingRequests
apRadiusClientExtAccountingRequests.description: The total number of RADIUS Accounting-Request packets sent since client start-up. This does not include retransmissions.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingRetransmissio.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingRetransmissions
apRadiusClientExtAccountingRetransmissio.description: The total number of RADIUS Accounting-Request packets retransmitted to the same server since client start-up. Retransmissions include retries where the Identifier and Acct-Delay have been updated.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingResponses.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingResponses
apRadiusClientExtAccountingResponses.description: The total number of RADIUS Accounting-Response packets received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccountingResp.name: apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccountingResponses
apRadiusClientExtMalformedAccountingResp.description: The total number of malformed RADIUS Accounting-Response packets received from this server since client start-up. Bad authenticators are not included as malformed access responses.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingBadAuthentica.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingBadAuthenticators
apRadiusClientExtAccountingBadAuthentica.description: The total number of RADIUS Accounting-Response packets which contained invalid authenticators received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingPendingReques.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingPendingRequests
apRadiusClientExtAccountingPendingReques.description: The total number of RADIUS Accounting-Request packets sent to this server that have not yet timed out or received a response. This variable is incremented when an Accounting-Request is sent and decremented due to a timeout or retransmission.

apRadiusClientExtAccountingTimeouts.name: apRadiusClientExtAccountingTimeouts
apRadiusClientExtAccountingTimeouts.description: The total number of accounting timeouts to this server since client startup. After a timeout the client may retry to the same server, send to a different server, or give up. A retry to the same server is counted as a retransmit as well as a timeout. A send to a different server is counted as an Accounting-Request as well as a timeout.

apRadiusClientExtUnknownType.name: apRadiusClientExtUnknownType
apRadiusClientExtUnknownType.description: The total number of RADIUS packets of unknown type which were received from this server since client start-up.

apRadiusClientExtTable.name: apRadiusClientExtTable
apRadiusClientExtTable.description: The table listing the RADIUS servers with which the client shares a secret.

apRadiusClientExtRadServerEntry.name: apRadiusClientExtRadServerEntry
apRadiusClientExtRadServerEntry.description: The information regarding a single RADIUS server with which the client shares a secret.

apRadiusClientExtRadServerAuthPort.name: apRadiusClientExtRadServerAuthPort
apRadiusClientExtRadServerAuthPort.description: The UDP port number on the Radius Server which to send Radius Authentication packets.

apRadiusClientExtRadServerAcctPort.name: apRadiusClientExtRadServerAcctPort
apRadiusClientExtRadServerAcctPort.description: The UDP port number on the Radius Server which to send Radius Accounting packets.

apRadiusClientExtRadServerSecret.name: apRadiusClientExtRadServerSecret
apRadiusClientExtRadServerSecret.description: This is the Radius Secret which is shared between this Radius Client and the Radius Server.

apRadiusClientExtStatus.name: apRadiusClientExtStatus
apRadiusClientExtStatus.description: This object is used to create and destroy a Radius Server instance.
